{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/KarakuriNinjaVR_media2_2_8.gif?t=1734141669\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the world of Karakuri Ninja VR with this exciting demo! Learn to wield powerful weapons and master ninjutsu as you face off against formidable enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo includes a tutorial stage and one route with four action-packed stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/KarakuriNinjaVR_media2_2_10.gif?t=1734141669\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each stage features a variety of weapons such as Japanese swords, kunai, and shuriken, as well as items that enhance weapons to advance the battle situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players who are skilled ninja can use special ninjutsu such as energy balls and aura shields.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/extras/KarakuriNinjaVR_media2_2_7.gif?t=1734141669\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, enemies also attack with fire and lightning ninjutsu. In a ninja fight, one must carefully observe the enemy's actions and never miss the moment to strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Karakuri Ninja VR, as you progress through the stages, more powerful enemies will appear. Hone your swordsmanship and ninjutsu skills and face them bravely.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325150/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734141669","background_raw":"ht